00:11:48.260 --> 00:11:49.260
(smeh)

00:11:49.260 --> 00:11:52.260
JO: Povsem običajno. V Angliji in Ameriki,

00:11:52.260 --> 00:11:54.260
v Angliji in Ameriki.

00:11:54.260 --> 00:11:56.260
Uganite, kako smo to popravili. Uganite, kaj je to popravilo.

00:11:56.260 --> 00:11:58.260
Dvakrat po eno učno uro.

00:11:59.260 --> 00:12:01.260
Otroke moramo v šolah začeti učiti

00:12:01.260 --> 00:12:04.260
o hrani in pika.

00:12:04.260 --> 00:12:09.260
(aplavz)

00:12:09.260 --> 00:12:11.260
Rad bi vam povedal nekaj,

00:12:11.260 --> 00:12:14.260
rad bi vam povedal nekaj, kar v bistvu

00:12:14.260 --> 00:12:17.260
